<div class="section-outter">
<!-- BEGIN ABOUT  -->
<section id="about">
    <div class="section-wrapper">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="title animatez" data-effect="fadeInDown">ABOUT</h2>
            <h4 class="subtitle animatez" data-effect="fadeInUp">How is your<span class="main-color"> score </span>calculated?</h4>
        </div>
        <hr class="title-break">
        
        <!-- Row of 2 values -->
        <div class="section-inner">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-4 mg-sm animatez col-sm-offset-2"data-effect="fadeInUp">
                        <i class="fa fa-clock-o fa-5x main-color"></i>
                        <h3>
                            <strong>Speed of Payment</strong>
                        </h3>
                        <p>A large portion of your score is based on how fast you pay back your friends. The faster you pay back your charges, the higher your score will grow.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4 mg-sm animated fadeInUp" data-effect="fadeInUp">
                        <i class="fa fa-headphones fa-5x main-color"></i>
                        <h3>
                            <strong>Volume of Payment</strong>
                        </h3>
                        <p>The more payments you make through Venmo the higher your score will be. The more you use Venmo, the more likely you are to use it again to fulfill a charge.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- End row of 2 -->

        <div class="spacer small"></div>

        <!-- Row of 3 -->
        <div class="section-inner">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-4 mg-sm animatez" data-effect="fadeInUp">
                        <i class="fa fa-money fa-5x main-color"></i>
                        <h3>
                            <strong>Outstanding Balance</strong>
                        </h3>
                        <p>The amount of money you owe at any given time can also lower your score. If you have any pending payments, they will negatively impact your score.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4 mg-sm animatez delay one" data-effect="fadeInUp">
                        <i class="fa fa-signal fa-5x main-color"></i>
                        <h3>
                            <strong>Uncharged Payments</strong>
                        </h3>
                        <p>If you're the kind of person that pays their friends without having to be asked, you will see that reflected positively on your score.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4 mg-sm animatez delay two" data-effect="fadeInUp">
                        <i class="fa fa-male fa-5x main-color"></i>
                        <h3>
                            <strong>Community Based</strong>
                        </h3>
                        <p>Your score is affected by the FiveEasyPayments community. Scores are calculated based on averages of user activity.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div> 
        <!-- End row of 3 -->
        <div class="spacer big"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
<!-- END ABOUT -->

